}
!}
max-cards: 4

#Choose a command area for the month. Congress handles bills and coalition votes, the White House handles executive strategy, and the party deck handles Democratic organization and outside-party relations. Easy mode gives an extra card slot each month.

[? if year = 1928 and month = 2 : The emergency transition is underway. Congress and the coalition are already maneuvering for control of the recovery agenda. ?]

- @congressional
- @presidential
- @party
- #advisor
- @shuffle_leadership_pinned


@party
title: Party Organization and Factions
subtitle: Campaigns, party machinery, faction fights, and SPA/Farmer-Labor relations.
card-image: img/Vorwaerts_nr_1.png
is-deck: true

- #party_affairs

@presidential
title: White House and Administration
subtitle: Executive messaging, cabinet direction, governors, courts, and national crisis management.
view-if: president_party = "SPD" or president_party = "DEM" or president_party = "Democratic Party"
card-image: img/reichstag_2.jpg
is-deck: true

- #presidential_affairs

@congressional
title: Congress, Coalition, and Policy
subtitle: Legislation, committee control, patronage, farm policy, labor policy, and bargaining.
card-image: img/reichstag_1.jpg
is-deck: true

- #congressional_affairs
